 was over the moon when <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/watch-a-goldfish-beat-the-hardest-boss-in-elden-ring-3465087">their pet goldfish triumphed over Malenia</a> in fewer attempts than their owner.</p><p> With the expansion <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/elden-ring-major-expansion-announced-shadow-of-the-erdtree-3405694"><em>Shadow of the Erdtree</em></a> on its way, it&#39;s doubtless that even more players will test their mettle against the brutal combat in new areas and with new weapons.</p><p> In other gaming news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/larian-studios">Larian Studios</a> wants <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/baldurs-gate-iii"><em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em></a> to be <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-looks-rad-on-steam-deck-will-be-verified-at-launch-3476389">Steam Deck Verified</a> in time for its launch because “it looks rad.”</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/streamer-completes-hitless-elden-ring-run-by-using-a-saxophone-3476459">Streamer completes “hitless” &#39;Elden Ring&#39; run by using a saxophone</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
